byline.original: By Densie Webb; Densie Webb, a freelance writer and editor, is a registered dietitian

docs.lead_paragraph: LEAD: SWEET dreams of guilt-free ice cream binges and all the cream cheese you can eat danced in consumers' heads when the Nutrasweet Company and Procter & Gamble announced many months ago that they had discovered low-calorie fat substitutes.
